name: Horimon 008 金魚;GOLD FISH
description:
Meaning : Lucky in money,  Protection, Strength, 

The goldfish is a symbol of luckiness with many meanings. As it has "gold" in the name, goldfishes are traditionally treated as the charm or lucky symbols for money luck in China and Japan. Goldfishes are also the symbol of having lots of children, since they lay many eggs. They are not tasty fish no matter how you cook them, which makes them also a symbol of strength. Black goldfish have the power of protecting you from bad luck.
